post_install() {
  cat <<'EOF'
roon-proton is installed.

For the recommended desktop-following output, load snd-aloop once with
"sudo modprobe snd-aloop pcm_substreams=1", then run "roon-proton setup" as
your desktop user. For a controller-only or non-systemd installation, run
"roon-proton setup desktop" instead. In Roon Settings > Audio, enable the first
Loopback PCM and name it "System Output (PipeWire)". Leave the second Loopback
PCM disabled.
EOF
}
